'''小犬座'''是[[北天_(天球)|北天]]小[[星座|星座]]，属公元二世纪[[克劳狄乌斯·托勒密|克劳狄乌斯·托勒密]]划分的48个星座，面积在88个现代星座排71位。[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]原名“{{lang|la|Canis Minor}}”意为“小犬”，与代表“大犬”的[[大犬座|大犬座]]对应，两犬都追随[[獵戶座|獵戶座]]代表的猎人。

小犬座只有两颗恒星亮度超过4.0[[视星等|视星等]]，其中[[南河三|南河三]]达0.34视星等，[[南河二|南河二]]2.9视星等。[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]为星座中八颗恒星[[拜耳命名法|分配希腊字母]]，[[約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德|約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德]]为14颗恒星编号。南河三距地球[[鄰近恆星列表|很近]]，亮度在夜空所有恒星排[[恆星亮度列表|第七]]，是有[[白矮星|白矮星]][[聯星|相伴]]的黄白[[主序星|主序星]]。南河二是蓝白主序星。[[魯坦星|魯坦星]]是九等[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]，也是小犬座除南河三外离[[太阳系|太阳系]]最近的恒星。四等星[[南河增八|南河增八]]已进入橙巨星阶段，[[恆星演化|演化周期]]走向尾声，2012年人类发现它还有行星。小犬座的[[深空天體|深空天體]]很少，每年12月上旬[[水位二|水位二]]附近有[[流星雨|流星雨]]。

== 历史与神话 ==
[[File:Cmi.jpg|thumb]]1801年《天图册》上的小犬座]]

小犬座最早见于[[美索不达米亚|美索不达米亚]]记录，与[[古典希臘時期|古典希臘時期]]的[[天体制图学|天体制图学]]传统关系密切。公元前1100年左右的《三星表》把南河三与南河二称为“双胞胎”（MASH.TAB.BA）。古巴比伦人后来的[[古巴比伦星表|规范星表]]《[[纲要_(古巴比伦)|纲要]]》（MUL.APIN）中“双胞胎”又指[[參旗六|參旗六]]、[[参旗七|参旗七]]、[[井宿七|井宿七]]和[[水府二|水府二]]。“双胞胎”的含义随之变化，意指[[巴比伦神话|巴比伦神话]]里的双面神袛卢拉尔（{{lang|en|Lulal}}）与拉塔拉克（{{lang|en|Latarak}}），两者实为一体，但性格截然相反。小犬座还曾得名“DAR.LUGAL”，位于“（猎户座）背后的恒星”，《纲要》中的小犬座代表[[鸡|公鸡]]，该名称还可能意指[[天兔座|天兔座]]。<ref name="rogers1998">{{cite journal | first = John H. | last = Rogers | year = 1998 | title = Origins of the Ancient Constellations: I. The Mesopotamian traditions | journal=Journal of the British Astronomical Association | volume = 108 | pages = 9–28 | bibcode = 1998JBAA..108....9R}}</ref>古巴比伦人把“DAR.LUGAL”称为“DAR.MUŠEN”或“DAR.LUGAL.MUŠEN”，[[阿卡德帝国|阿卡德人]]把小犬座称为“tarlugallu”<ref>{{cite journal | title = Astral Magic in Babylonia | journal = Transactions of the American Philosophical Society | series = New Series | volume = 85 | issue = 4 |year = 1995 | last = Reiner | first = Erica | pages = i–150 | jstor = 1006642 | doi = 10.2307/1006642}}</ref>。

[[克劳狄乌斯·托勒密|克劳狄乌斯·托勒密]]二世纪的著作《[[天文學大成|天文學大成]]》划有48个星座，其中小犬座只有两颗恒星，不像其他绝大多数星座那样包含[[星群|星群]]。[[古希臘語|古希臘語]]把小犬座称为“{{lang|grc|προκυων}}”，意为“在狗以前”，[[西塞罗|西塞罗]]等人将辞汇音译成[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]“{{lang|la|Antecanis}}”、“{{lang|la|Praecanis}}”及其他变体。罗马文献还为名称加上形容词“{{lang|la|parvus}}”，意为“小”，因为星座比较黯淡，“{{lang|la|septentrionalis}}”意为“北面”，因为星座在[[大犬座|大犬座]]北面，还有“{{lang|la|primus}}”，意指星座率先升起，“{{lang|la|sinister}}”意指星座从左边升起。<ref name="allen">{{cite book | last = Allen | first = Richard Hinckley | year = 1963 | orig-year = 1899 | title = Star Names: Their Lore and Meaning | edition = corrected | publisher = Dover Publications | location = Mineola, New York | isbn = 978-0-486-21079-7 | page = [https://archive.org/details/starnamestheirlo00alle/page/383 383] | url = https://archive.org/details/starnamestheirlo00alle | access-date = 2021-03-09}}</ref>[[希腊神话|希腊神话]]有时把小犬座与[[透墨索斯恶狐|透墨索斯恶狐]]联系起来，据称[[宙斯|宙斯]]把它和抓捕它的神犬[[莱拉普斯|莱拉普斯]]（{{lang|grc|Λαῖλαψ}}，意为“飓风”）变成石头放在天国，其中莱拉普斯就是大犬座，透墨索斯恶狐是小犬座<ref>Apollodorus, [[書庫|Bibliotheca]] 3,192.</ref><ref>{{cite book | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=yMbzhPrIkt4C&pg=PA275&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | title = Nature Guide Stars and Planets | page = 275 | author = DK Publishing | publisher = Penguin | year = 2012 | isbn = 978-1-4654-0353-7 | access-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074519/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=yMbzhPrIkt4C&pg=PA275&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[埃拉托斯特尼|埃拉托斯特尼]]将小犬座与猎户座联系起来，意指小狗陪伴猎人；[[许癸努斯|许癸努斯]]把小犬座与雅典人伊卡里俄斯（{{lang|grc|Ἰκάριος}}）的狗麦拉（{{lang|grc|Μαῖρα}}，意为“烟火”）联系起来<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Klepešta | first1 = Josef | last2 = Rükl | first2 = Antonín | title = Constellations | publisher = Hamlyn | location = London, England | year = 1974 | orig-year = 1969 | access-date = 2021-03-09 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/constellationsco0000klep/page/118 118–119] | isbn = 978-0-600-00893-4 | url = https://archive.org/details/constellationsco0000klep/page/118}}</ref><ref name="ridpath star tales" />。得知伊卡里俄斯去世后，麦拉与主人之女[[厄里戈涅|厄里戈涅]]（{{lang|grc|Ἠριγόνη}}）自尽身亡，他们后来都在天上拥有一席之地，厄里戈涅是[[室女座|室女座]]，伊卡里俄斯是[[牧夫座|牧夫座]]<ref name="ridpath star tales">{{cite web |url = http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/canisminor.html | last = Ridpath | first = Ian | title = Canis Minor | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201222232711/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/canisminor.html | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-09 | work = Star Tales | archive-date = 2020-12-22}}</ref>。为感谢麦拉的忠诚，天神把小犬座放在银河“岸边”，古人相信银河便是天河，所以麦拉永远不会口渴<ref name="Chartrand">{{cite book | author = Mark R. Chartrand III | year = 1982 | title = Skyguide: A Field Guide for Amateur Astronomers | page = 126 | isbn = 0-307-13667-1}}</ref>。古埃及将小犬座视为胡狼头神[[阿努比斯|阿努比斯]]<ref name="Chartrand" />。

[[中古伊斯蘭天文學|中世纪阿拉伯天文学家]]将小犬座写作“{{lang|ar|al-Kalb al-Asghar}}”，代表狗；[[阿卜杜勒-拉赫曼·苏菲|阿卜杜勒-拉赫曼·苏菲]]的《[[恆星之書|恆星之書]]》就有星座与犬科动物重叠的图像<ref name="upton">{{cite journal | pages = 179–197 [195–196] | title = A Manuscript of "The Book of the Fixed Stars" by ʿAbd Ar-Raḥmān Aṣ-Ṣūfī | first = Joseph M. | last = Upton | journal = Metropolitan Museum Studies | volume = 4 | issue = 2 | date = 1933-03 | jstor = 1522800 | doi = 10.2307/1522800}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | pages = 1–26 [Plate 12] | first = Emmy | last = Wellesz | title = An Early al-Ṣūfī Manuscript in the Bodleian Library in Oxford: A Study in Islamic Constellation Images | journal = Ars Orientalis | year = 1959 | volume = 3 | jstor = 4629096}}</ref>。托勒密和阿拉伯人所称的小犬座略有不同，阿拉伯人把现属[[獵戶座|獵戶座]]的[[軍市一|軍市一]]划入小犬座，代表狗项圈。南河三与南河二的阿拉伯语名称不是古希腊语直译，但都意指它们与[[天狼星|天狼星]]接近且类似。南河三的阿拉伯语名称是“{{lang|ar|ash-Shi'ra ash-Shamiya}}”，意为“叙利亚西里斯”（西里斯是天狼星的音译）；南河二称“{{lang|ar|ash-Shira al-Ghamisa}}”，指“睡眼惺忪的西里斯”。<ref name="upton" />[[突尼西亞|突尼西亞]]牧羊人发现六个星座代表炎热的旱季，其中包括大犬座和小犬座恒星的称为“Merzem”，预示接下来两周天气炎热<ref>{{cite journal | title = A Review of African Ethno-Astronomy: With Particular Reference to Saharan Livestock-Keepers | last = Oxby | first = Claire | journal = La Ricerca Folklorica | date = October 1999 | pages = 57–58 | jstor = 1479768 | issue = 40 | doi = 10.2307/1479768}}</ref>。
[[File:Sidney_Hall_-_Urania's_Mirror_-_Monoceros,_Canis_Minor,_and_Atelier_Typographique.jpg|thumb]]，下方是已作废的[[印刷室座|印刷室座]]]]

小犬座还有其他名称：[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]在17世纪初为星座起名“Fovea”，意指“坑”，或是意为“桑树”的“Morus”。17世纪日耳曼诗人兼作家[[菲利普·冯·泽森|菲利普·泽森]]（{{lang|de|Philipp Zesen}}）把小犬座和《[[經外書|經外書]]》里托比亚斯（{{lang|en|Tobias}}）的狗联系起来<ref name="allen" />。[[理查德·普罗克特|理查德·普罗克特]]（{{lang|en|Richard A. Proctor}}）1870年把小犬座称为“猫”（{{lang|la|Felis}}），大犬座还是称为“犬”（{{lang|la|Canis}}）<ref name="allen" />，自称是为缩短名称，方便[[星圖|天体图]]上标识<ref>{{cite book | last = Proctor | first = Richard Anthony | year = 1870 | title = A Star Atlas for the Library, the School and the Observatory | publisher = Longmans, Green | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=yzRRAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA17&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | location = London, England | pages = 16–17 | access-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074530/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=yzRRAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA17&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，也有文献把小犬座与大犬座混淆，起名“猎户座的狗”（{{lang|la|Canis Orionis}}）<ref>{{cite book | page = [https://archive.org/details/outerspacemythsn00jobe/page/137 137] | title = Outer Space : Myths, Name Meanings, Calendars from the Emergence of History to the Present Day | url = https://archive.org/details/outerspacemythsn00jobe | last1 = Jobes | first1 = Gertrude | last2 = Jobes | first2 = James | year = 1964 | publisher = Scarecrow Press | location = New York, New York | oclc = 882705}}</ref>。

[[中国天文学史|中国天文学]]将小犬座恒星划入[[朱雀|南方朱雀]]。南河三、南河二和南河一组成[[南河_(星官)|南河]][[星官|星官]]，南河意为银河以东、[[井宿|井宿]]南面的河流。<ref name="ridpath star tales" /><ref>{{cite web | author1 = 陳冠中 | author2 = 陳輝樺 |url = http://aeea.nmns.edu.tw/2006/0607/ap060716.html | publisher = AEEA (Activities of Exhibition and Education in Astronomy) | title = 天文教育資訊網 | date = 2006-07-16 | access-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105162811/http://aeea.nmns.edu.tw/2006/0607/ap060716.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-11-05}}</ref>与南河对应的是[[北河_(星官)|北河]]，包含双子座恒星[[北河二|北河二]]、[[北河三|北河三]]和[[北河一|北河一]]，[[黄道|黄道]]在南河与北河间通过，故而两条河又代表黄道大门。小犬座的[[水位一|水位一]]、[[水位二|水位二]]与[[巨蟹座|巨蟹座]]的[[水位三|水位三]]、[[水位四|水位四]]组成星官[[水位_(星官)|水位]]，与[[双子座|双子座]]恒星一起代表负责监控水位、泄洪的官员，或是测量水位的工具。<ref name="ridpath star tales" />古代朝鲜将小犬座四颗恒星划入南方朱雀内的“水位座”<ref>{{cite journal | title = A Korean Star Map | last1 = Rufus | first1 = W. Karl | last2 = Chao | first2 = Celia | pages = 316–326 | journal = Isis | volume = 35 | issue = 4 | date = Autumn 1944 | jstor = 330843 | doi = 10.1086/358723}}</ref>。

[[波利尼西亚人|波利尼西亚人]]通常不将小犬座视为星座，但很重视南河三，经常为它命名。[[土阿莫土群岛|土阿莫土群岛]]将小犬座称为“Hiro”，意为“像椰子纤维线条般扭曲”；还有“Kopu-nui-o-Hiro”，意为“像椰子纤维线条般扭曲的大肚子”，可能是代表小犬座的现代人物名，或南河三的别名。[[库克群岛|库克群岛]]第二大的[[曼加伊亚岛|曼加伊亚岛]]以[[女神|女神]]之名把小犬座称为“维纳”（Vena），[[新西兰|新西兰]]把星座称为“Puanga-hori”，其中“Puanga”是[[參宿七|參宿七]]的名字，“Puanga-hori”可以理解成“假参宿七”。[[社會群島|社會群島]]把南河三称为“Ana-tahua-vahine-o-toa-te-manava”，字面意为“心灵勇敢的女祭司阿斯特”，喻意“雄辩的支柱”。<ref>{{cite book| last = Makemson | first = Maud Worcester | year = 1941 | publisher = Yale University Press | location = New Haven, Connecticut | title = The Morning Star Rises: An Account of Polynesian Astronomy | pages = 199, 209, 247, 267, 280 | bibcode = 1941msra.book.....M}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Tahitian Astronomy: Birth of the Heavenly Bodies | last = Henry | first = Teuira | journal = The Journal of the Polynesian Society | volume = 16 | issue = 2 | pages= 101–04 | date = 1907-06 | jstor = 20700813}}</ref>澳大利亚[[北領地|北領地]]原住民[[瓦达曼人|瓦达曼人]]把南河三与南河二分别称为“Magum”和“Gurumana”，是变成[[桉树|桉树]]的先祖，皮肤变成树皮后，他们还能通过摇动树叶发出人说话的声音<ref name="darksparklers">{{cite book | last1 = Harney | first1 = Bill Yidumduma | last2 = Cairns | first2 = Hugh C. | title = Dark Sparklers | publisher = Hugh C. Cairns | location = Merimbula, New South Wales | year = 2004 | orig-year = 2003 | edition = Revised | page = 142 | isbn = 978-0-9750908-0-0}}</ref>。[[阿兹特克历法|阿兹特克历法]]与阿兹特克宇宙学关系密切，将小犬座恒星与猎户座和双子座部分恒星连成[[星群|星群]]，与名为“水”的日期关联<ref>{{cite journal | title = Calendar Animals and Deities | last = Kelley | first = David H. | pages = 317–337 [333] | journal = Southwestern Journal of Anthropology | volume = 16 | issue = 3 | date = Autumn 1960 | doi = 10.1086/soutjanth.16.3.3629035 | jstor = 3629035}}</ref>。

== 简介 ==
小犬座位于双子座明亮恒星北河二与北河三正南面<ref name="sky">{{cite book | last = Newell | first = W.J. | title = The Australian Sky | publisher = Jacaranda Press | location = Brisbane, Queensland | year = 1970 | orig-year = 1965 | page = 53 | oclc = 7053675}}</ref>，南接[[麒麟座|麒麟座]]，北靠双子座，东挨[[长蛇座|长蛇座]]，东北与巨蟹座接壤，与大犬座不直接相邻，中间隔着麒麟座。小犬座覆盖183平方度夜空，在88个星座排名第71，每年冬季在[[北半球|北半球]]夜空南面最为显著。<ref name="garfinkle1997">{{cite book | first = Robert A. | last = Garfinkle | title = Star-hopping: Your Visa to Viewing the Universe | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, England | year = 1997 | pages = 78–81 | isbn = 978-0-521-59889-7}}</ref>比利时天文学家[[尤金·德爾波特|尤金·德爾波特]]1930年正式划分星座边界，小犬座呈14条边组成的多边形（见文首信息框）。星座在[[赤道坐標系統|赤道坐標系統]]的[[赤经|赤经]]位于{{RA|07|06.4}}至{{RA|08|11.4}}范围，[[赤纬|赤纬]]在{{dec|13.22}}到{{dec|−0.36}}之间。<ref name="boundary" />小犬座在一到三月夜空比较容易看到<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Ellyard | first1 = David | last2 = Tirion | first2 = Wil | year = 2008 | title = The Southern Sky Guide | edition = 3rd | orig-year = 1993 | page = 4 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=5Gn0ivM4EK0C&pg=PA4&redir_esc=y | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Port Melbourne, Victoria | isbn = 978-0-521-71405-1 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074606/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=5Gn0ivM4EK0C&pg=PA4&redir_esc=y | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并以二月中旬晚上十点左右最清晰<ref>{{cite book | title = The Monthly Sky Guide | url = https://archive.org/details/monthlyskyguidet00ridp | last1 = Ridpath | first1 = Ian | last2 = Tirion | first2 = Wil | date = 2006-11-13 | edition = 7th | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, England | pages = [https://archive.org/details/monthlyskyguidet00ridp/page/n21 21]–22 | isbn = 978-0-521-68435-4}}</ref>。此后直到七月只在日落后一小段时间可见，消失后又在黎明前升到天上<ref>{{cite web | url = http://rasnz.org.nz/Stars/Canis.htm | title = Canis Major and Canis Minor, 2 Constellations for February | last = Rodmell | first = Paul | publisher = Royal Astronomical Society of New Zealand | access-date = 2015-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150219023252/http://rasnz.org.nz/Stars/Canis.htm | dead-url = yes | archive-date = 2015-02-19}}</ref>。1922年，[[國際天文聯會|國際天文聯會]]确定以三字母缩写“{{lang|la|CMi}}”代表小犬座<ref name="pa30_469">{{cite journal | last = Russell | first = Henry Norris | title = The New International Symbols for the Constellations | journal = [[通俗天文學_(美國雜誌)|Popular Astronomy]] | volume = 30 | pages = 469–471 | bibcode = 1922PA.....30..469R | year = 1922}}</ref>。

== 显著特点 ==

=== 恒星 ===
[[File:CanisMinorCC.jpg|thumb]]
{{see also|小犬座恒星列表}}
小犬座只有两颗恒星亮度超过4.0[[视星等|视星等]]，其中南河三达0.34视星等<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=CCDM%20J07393%2B0514%20A | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727081012/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=CCDM%20J07393%2B0514%20A | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | title = Procyon AB – Spectroscopic Binary | publisher = SIMBAD}}</ref>，在夜空所有恒星排[[恆星亮度列表|第七]]，而且距地球[[鄰近恆星列表|非常近]]。南河三又名“Procyon”，源自古希腊语，意为“在狗以前”，意指该星是在人称“狗星”的大犬座天狼星前约一小时升起。南河三属[[聯星|联星系]]，主星称为南河三A，是光谱等级F5 IV-V的黄白[[主序星|主序星]]<ref name="ridpath">{{cite book | first1 = Ian | last1 = Ridpath | first2 = Wil | last2 = Tirion | year = 2001 | title = Stars and Planets Guide | publisher = Princeton University Press | location = Princeton, New Jersey | isbn = 978-0-691-08913-3 | pages = 100–101}}</ref>，与光谱等级DA的黯淡[[白矮星|白矮星]]南河三B相伴。南河三B亮度10.7视星等，以41年公转周期围绕质量更大的南河三A运转。<ref name="ridpath" />南河三A有1.4倍[[太阳质量|太阳质量]]，南河三B仅0.6倍<ref name=aj131>{{cite journal | last1 = Gatewood | first1 = George | last2 = Han | first2 = Inwoo | title = An Astrometric Study of Procyon | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomical-journal_2006-02_131_2/page/1015 | journal = Astronomical Journal | volume = 131 | issue = 2 | pages = 1015–1021 | year = 2006 | doi = 10.1086/498894 | bibcode = 2006AJ....131.1015G}}</ref>，联星系距[[地球|地球]]11.4光年，在亮度超过1.0视星等的北天恒星中离地最近<ref name="ridpath" /><ref>{{cite book | title = The Cambridge Encyclopedia of Stars | page = 63 | last = Kaler | first = James B. | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 2006 | location = Cambridge, England | isbn = 978-0-521-81803-2}}</ref>。2.89视星等的[[南河二|南河二]]是小犬座第二亮恒星，距[[太阳系|太阳系]]160±10光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2beta">{{cite DR2|3143264535611161088}}</ref>，是光谱等级B8 Ve的蓝白[[主序星|主序星]]<ref name="betvar">{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200928030148/https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5638 | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5638 | title = Bet CMi | publisher = American Association of Variable Star Observers | work = International Variable Star Index | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-09-28 | date = 2010-01-04}}</ref>。它亮度远不及南河三，但实际[[光度|光度]]要高得多，有三倍太阳质量，250倍太阳光度<ref name="Kalerbeta">{{Cite journal | first = Jim | last = Kaler | journal = Stars | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105104432/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/gomeisa.html | title = Gomeisa (Beta Canis Minoris) | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/gomeisa.html | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-11-05}}</ref>。南河二的亮度在2.84到2.92视星等范围变化，幅度很小，科学家将它归入[[殼層星|殼層星]]（仙后座γ型变星）<ref name="betvar" />。星体周围是气体圆盘，经恒星加热并发出辐射<ref name="Kalerbeta" />。

[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]用α到η共七个希腊字母为小犬座最明显的八颗恒星命名，其中两颗星合用字母δ，分别是δ<sup>1</sup>和δ<sup>2</sup><ref name="Wagman-2003">{{cite book | last = Wagman | first = Morton | year = 2003 | title = Lost Stars: Lost, Missing and Troublesome Stars from the Catalogues of Johannes Bayer, Nicholas Louis de Lacaille, John Flamsteed, and Sundry Others | publisher = The McDonald & Woodward Publishing Company | location = Blacksburg, [[弗吉尼亚州|VA]] | isbn = 978-0-939923-78-6}}</ref>{{rp|76–77}}。[[約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德|約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德]]为14颗星编号，还把其中一颗称为δ<sup>3</sup><ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|77}}，不过，后人找不到他编号的小犬座12<ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|369}}。拜耳1603年的《[[測天圖|測天圖]]》将南河三画在狗肚，南河二位于颈部<ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|504}}。附近的[[南河增一|南河增一]]、[[南河一|南河一]]与[[南河增二|南河增二]]分别代表狗的脖子、头顶和胸口<ref name="kambic" /><ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|504}}。南河增一是光谱等级K3-III C的K型橙[[巨星|巨星]]，离地318光年，亮度4.34视星等<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727074525/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Gamma+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Gamma+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = Gamma Canis Minoris | publisher = SIMBAD}}</ref>，用双筒望远镜可以明显看出星体色彩<ref name="kambic">{{cite book | last = Kambič | first = Bojan | title = Viewing the Constellations with Binoculars: 250+ Wonderful Sky Objects to See and Explore | publisher = Springer | location = New York, New York | year = 2009 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=3vxLNPNHOcwC&pg=PA233&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | page = 32 | isbn = 978-0-387-85354-3 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074631/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=3vxLNPNHOcwC&pg=PA233&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。南河增一包含的星体众多，主星南河增一A是[[聯星|光谱联星]]，另有有三颗光学伴星，分别是13等的南河增一B，12等的南河增一C和10等南河增一D。南河增一A的两颗星体以389.2天为周期围绕彼此旋转，呈偏心轨道，间距在2.3到1.4[[天文單位|天文單位]]变化。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/gammacmi.html | title = Gamma Canis Minoris | last = Kaler | first = Jim | work = Star of the Week | access-date = 2021-03-10 | date = 2010-03-19 | archive-date = 2016-11-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161104144004/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/gammacmi.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>南河一是光谱等级G6.5IIb的黄色[[亮巨星|亮巨星]]，亮度4.99视星等<ref>{{cite web | publisher = SIMBAD | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727075417/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Epsilon+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Epsilon+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = Epsilon Canis Minoris}}</ref>，距地球730至810光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2eps">{{cite DR2|3155451625572457344}}</ref>，直径和光度分别是太阳13倍和750倍<ref name="bagnall">{{cite book | last = Bagnall | first = Philip M. | title = The Star Atlas Companion: What You Need to Know about the Constellations | publisher = Springer | location = New York, New York | year = 2012 | isbn = 978-1-4614-0830-7 | pages = 108–112 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=KcIg02TKW6QC&pg=PA110&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308085522/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=KcIg02TKW6QC&pg=PA110&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。南河增二是光谱等级F0III的巨星，亮度5.24视星等<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200816011524/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Eta+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-08-16 | dead-url = no | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Eta+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = Eta Canis Minoris | publisher = SIMBAD | access-date = 2021-03-10}}</ref>，使用双筒望远镜可以看到黄色光泽和11.1视星等的黯淡伴星<ref name="garfinkle1997" /><ref>{{cite book | author1 = David Malin | author2 = David J. Frew | title = Hartung's Astronomical Objects for Southern Telescopes: A Handbook for Amateur Observers | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, England | year = 1995 | page = 184 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=EQAYGmZT0o8C&pg=PA183&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2021-03-10 | isbn = 978-0-521-55491-6 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074711/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=EQAYGmZT0o8C&pg=PA183&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>，伴星与主星相隔四[[弧秒|弧秒]]，距离440天文单位，公转周期约五千年<ref name="kalereta">{{cite web | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/etacmi.html | title = Eta and Delta-1 CMi | last = Kaler | first = Jim | work = Stars | publisher = University of Illinois | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105143203/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/etacmi.html | archive-date = 2020-11-05 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

南河三附近有三颗恒星共称小犬座δ，其中δ<sup>1</sup>又名[[南河增五|南河增五]]，是5.25视星等的F型黄白巨星，离地约790光年，光度和质量分别是太阳360倍和3.75倍，因年代古老已开始膨胀并冷却，生命周期大部分时间是光谱等级B6V的[[B型主序星|B型主序星]]<ref name="kalereta" />。δ<sup>2</sup>又称[[南河增四|南河增四]]，是光谱等级F2V的[[黃-白矮星|F型黄白巨星]]，距地球136光年<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200816011535/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=8+CMi | archive-date = 2020-08-16 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=8+CMi | title = 8 Canis Minoris | publisher = SIMBAD}}</ref>。δ<sup>3</sup>又名南河增三，是光谱等级A0Vnn的[[A型主序星|白主序星]]，亮度5.83视星等，离地680光年<ref>{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=9+CMi | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200802134021/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=9+CMi | title = 9 Canis Minoris | publisher = SIMBAD | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-08-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。这三颗星代表狗的左后腿，5.13视星等的[[南河增六|南河增六]]是右后腿<ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|504}}<ref name="simbadzeta" />。南河增六是光谱等级B8II的蓝白亮巨星，距太阳系623光年<ref name="simbadzeta">{{cite web | title = Zeta Canis Minoris | publisher = SIMBAD | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200802134844/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Zeta+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-08-02 | dead-url = no | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Zeta+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id}}</ref>。

离地222±7光年的橙巨星[[南河增八|南河增八]]亮度4.39视星等<ref name="exoplanet">{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727064821/http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/hd_66141_b/ | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | url = http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/hd_66141_b/ | title = Planet HD 66141 b | last = Zolotukhin | first = Ivan | year = 2012 | work = Exoplanet.eu | publisher = Paris Observatory | access-date = 2021-03-10}}</ref><ref name="Gaia-DR2lam">{{cite DR2|3087964941887693056}}</ref>，已有68亿年历史，光谱等级K2III，直径约为太阳22倍，质量1.1倍，光度174倍，[[絕對星等|絕對星等]]−0.15<ref name="Lee">{{Cite journal | title = Detection of an Exoplanet Around the Evolved K Giant HD 66141 | arxiv = 1211.2054 | year = 2012 | journal = Astronomy & Astrophysics | volume = 548 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201118014 | last1 = Lee | first = B.-C. | last2 = Mkrtichian | first2 = D. E. | last3 = Han | first3 = I. | last4 = Park | first4 = M.-G. | last5 = Kim | first5 = K.-M. | pages = A118 | bibcode = 2012A&A...548A.118L}}</ref>。历史上的天体制图师曾在星图上标错南河增八位置，导致人们误以为它是[[船尾座|船尾座]]恒星并以“船尾座13”命名，波得曾为该星命名“小犬座λ”，现已不再使用<ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|460}}。2012年，人们通过测量恒星[[徑向速度|徑向速度]]发现南河增八的行星，质量约为[[木星|木星]]六倍，[[轨道周期|轨道周期]]480天<ref name="exoplanet" />。

[[小犬座BC|小犬座BC]]是光谱等级M4III的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]，离太阳系约五百光年<ref name="Tabur">{{cite journal | title = Long-term Photometry and Periods for 261 Nearby Pulsating M Giants | last1 = Tabur | first1 = V. | last2 = Bedding | first2 = T. R. | year = 2009 | journal = [[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 400 | issue = 4 | pages = 1945–1961 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2009.15588.x | last3 = Kiss | first3 = L. L. | last4 = Moon | first4 = T. T. | last5 = Szeidl | first5 = B. | last6 = Kjeldsen | first6 = H. | arxiv = 0908.3228 | bibcode = 2009MNRAS.400.1945T}}</ref>，是亮度在6.14到6.42视星等变化的[[半規則變星|半規則變星]]<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924191843/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5595 | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5595 | title = BC CMi | publisher = American Association of Variable Star Observers | work = International Variable Star Index | access-date = 2021-03-10 | date = 2009-08-25 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-09-24}}</ref>，已发现27.7天、143.3天和208.3天三种变化周期<ref name="Tabur" />。

[[小犬座AZ|小犬座AZ]]、小犬座AD和小犬座BI都是[[矮造父變星|矮造父變星]]，脉冲间距短至不超过六小时，用于充当[[宇宙距离尺度|宇宙距离尺度]]，是[[星震學|星震學]]研究的重要目标<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsots_delsct | title = Delta Scuti and the Delta Scuti Variables | last = Templeton | first = Matthew | date = 2010-07-16 | work = Variable Star of the Season | publisher = AAVSO (American Association of Variable Star Observers) | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210216153810/https://www.aavso.org/vsots_delsct | archive-date = 2021-10-21}}</ref>。小犬座AZ光谱等级A5IV<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=AZ+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = V* AZ Canis Minoris – Variable of Delta Scuti type | publisher = SIMBAD | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727065707/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=AZ+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27}}</ref>，亮度以2.3小时为周期在6.44到6.51视星等变动<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5593 | title = AZ CMi | publisher = AAVSO | work = International Variable Star Index | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727071551/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5593 | date = 2010-01-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。小犬座AD光谱等级F2III<ref>{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=AD+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = V* AD Canis Minoris – Variable of Delta Scuti type | publisher = SIMBAD | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727071613/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=AD+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，亮度以2.95小时周期在9.21至9.51视星等闪烁<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727064945/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5572 | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5572 | title = AD Canis Minoris | publisher = AAVSO | work = International Variable Star Index | access-date = 2021-03-10 | date = 2010-01-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-27}}</ref>。小犬座BI光谱等级F2，亮度9.19视星等左右<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=BI+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = V* BI Canis Minoris – Variable of Delta Scuti type | publisher = SIMBAD | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727071048/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=BI+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，变动周期约2.91小时<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5601 | title = BI Canis Minoris | publisher = AAVSO | work = International Variable Star Index | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727065450/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5601 | date = 2011-02-02 | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

小犬座至少三颗红巨星是[[刍藁变星|刍藁变星]]。其中光谱等级M7e的[[小犬座S|小犬座S]]最亮<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727064958/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=S+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=S+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = S Canis Minoris | publisher = SIMBAD | access-date = 2021-03-10}}</ref>，以332.94天为周期在6.6至13.2视星等范围变化<ref name="garfinkle1997" /><ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200804180115/https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5516 | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=5516 | title = S CMi | publisher = AAVSO | dead-url = no | work = International Variable Star Index | date = 2010-01-04 | archive-date = 2020-08-04}}</ref>。小犬座V以336.1天周期在7.4到15.1视星等闪烁。小犬座R是[[S-型星|S-型星]]，亮度以337.8天周期在7.3至11.6视星等范围变化。<ref>{{cite book | title = Patrick Moore's Data Book of Astronomy | url = https://archive.org/details/patrickmooresdat00moor | last1 = Moore | first1 = Patrick | last2 = Rees | first2 = Robin | page = [https://archive.org/details/patrickmooresdat00moor/page/396 396] | isbn = 978-0-521-89935-2 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 2011}}</ref>

[[小犬座YZ|小犬座YZ]]是光谱等级M4.5V、亮度11.2视星等的[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=YZ+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = V* YZ Canis Minoris – Variable of BY Draconis Type | publisher = SIMBAD | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727095107/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=YZ+Canis+Minoris&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，离地20光年，尺寸约为木星三倍。小犬座YZ属[[耀星|耀星]]，不定时爆发持续几分钟的能量，强烈程度可能远超[[耀斑|耀斑]]<ref name="First flares">{{cite journal | title = First Flares on a Distant Star | journal = New Scientist | date = 1982-02-04 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=XQwcxTIERmUC&pg=PA305&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | page = 305 | last = Information | first = Reed Business | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074852/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=XQwcxTIERmUC&pg=PA305&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[魯坦星|魯坦星]]是光谱等级M3.5V的红矮星，亮度只有9.9视星等所以肉眼无法观测<ref name="RECONS">{{cite web | title = The One Hundred Nearest Stars | date = 2012-01-01 | publisher = Georgia State University Astronomy | archive-date = 2014-08-11 | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.chara.gsu.edu/RECONS/TOP100.posted.htm | location = Atlanta, Georgia | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140811021409/http://www.chara.gsu.edu/RECONS/TOP100.posted.htm | access-date = 2014-08-11}}</ref>，离地仅12.39光年，是小犬座除南河三外最近的恒星<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727090500/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=GJ+273&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=GJ+273&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = LHS 33 – High Proper-motion Star | publisher = SIMBAD | access-date = 2021-03-10}}</ref>。PSS 544-7是质量约为太阳两成的18等红矮星，离地685光年，1991年发现，估计是冲出[[星团|星团]]的炮弹星，如今还在迅速远离[[星系盤|星系盤]]<ref>{{cite journal | first1 = Carlos | last1 = de la Fuente Marcos | last2 = de la Fuente Marcos | first2 = Raúl | title = A Cannonball Star Candidate in Canis Minor | journal = New Astronomy | volume = 10 | issue = 7 | pages = 551–559 | doi = 10.1016/j.newast.2005.04.001 | year = 2005 | bibcode = 2005NewA...10..551D}}</ref>。

小犬座DY又名VSX J074727.6+065050，是[[天箭座WZ|天箭座WZ]]型[[矮新星|矮新星]]，亮度在2008年1至2月达到顶峰11.4视星等，此后约80天下降八等，亮度降至19.5视星等左右。小犬座DY是离地非常遥远的联星，白矮星和质量不及的恒星相互围绕旋转，白矮星还因间距很近持续吸收伴星物质并形成[[吸积盘|吸积盘]]，吸积过程逐渐积累直到急剧喷发。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Shears | first1 = Jeremy | last2 = Brady | first2 = Steve | last3 = Bolt | first3 = Greg | last4 = Campbell | first4 = Tut | last5 = Collins | first5 = Donald F. | last6 = Cook | first6 = Lewis M. | last7 = Crawford | first7 = Timothy R. | last8 = Koff | first8 = Robert | last9 = Krajci | first9 = Tom | last10 = McCormick | first10 = Jennie | last11 = Nelson | first11 = Peter | last12 = Patterson | first12 = Joseph | last13 = Ponthière | first13 = Pierre de | last14 = Potter | first14 = Mike | last15 = Rea | first15 = Robert | last16 = Roberts | first16 = George | last17 = Sabo | first17 = Richard | last18 = Staels | first18 = Bart | last19 = Vanmunster | first19 = Tonny | year = 2009 | title = VSX J074727.6+065050: A New WZ Sagittae Star in Canis Minor | journal = Journal of the British Astronomical Association | volume = 119 | issue = 6 | pages = 340–346 | arxiv = 0905.0061 | bibcode = 2009JBAA..119..340S}}</ref>

=== 深空天体 ===
[[File:Red_and_Long_Dead_Abell_24.tif|thumb]]星云<ref>{{cite web | title = Red and Long Dead | url = https://www.eso.org/public/images/potw1927a/ | publisher = European Southern Observatory | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200806083144/https://eso.org/public/images/potw1927a/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-08-06 | access-date = 2021-03-10}}</ref>]]

[[银河系|银河系]]跨过大半小犬座，但星座内的[[深空天體|深空天體]]很少<ref name="inglis">{{cite book | last = Inglis | first = Mike | title = Astronomy of the Milky Way: Observer's Guide to the Southern Sky | publisher = Springer | location = New York, New York | year = 2004 | page = 20 | isbn = 978-1-85233-742-1 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=1r0qvMjSCGAC&pg=SA2-PA9&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074912/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=1r0qvMjSCGAC&pg=SA2-PA9&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[威廉·赫歇爾|威廉·赫歇爾]]1786年的《[[星雲和星團總表|星雲和星團總表]]》记有四个，其中两个他误以为是星团<ref name="bratton">{{cite book | last = Bratton | first = Mark | title = The Complete Guide to the Herschel Objects: Sir William Herschel's Star Clusters, Nebulae and Galaxies | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, England | year = 2011 | page = 134 | isbn = 978-0-521-76892-4 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=JLuv9bAUbBwC&pg=PA134&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308074918/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=JLuv9bAUbBwC&pg=PA134&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。NGC 2459由五颗13到14等星组成，看起来相互接近，但实际没有关联<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121001935/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc24a.htm#2459 | url = http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc24a.htm#2459 | title = NGC Objects: NGC 2450 – 2499 | work = Celestial Atlas | last = Seligman | first = Courtney | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2021-01-21}}</ref>。NGC 2394情况类似<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc23a.htm#2394 | title = NGC Objects: NGC 2350 – 2399 | work = Celestial Atlas | last = Seligman | first = Courtney | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210122061213/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc23a.htm#2394 | archive-date = 2021-01-22}}</ref>，由15颗没有关联的恒星组成，其中最亮的是九等星<ref name="bratton" />。

赫歇爾还发现三个更加黯淡的星系，其中两个在相互影响<ref name="bratton" />。NGC 2508是13等[[透鏡狀星系|透鏡狀星系]]，估计离地2.05亿光年，直径八万光年<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc25.htm#2508 | title = NGC Objects: NGC 2500 – 2549 | work = Celestial Atlas | last = Seligman | first = Courtney | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020161940/https://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc25.htm#2508 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-10-20}}</ref>。赫歇爾以为NGC 2402是单个天体，实际上是几乎相邻并相互影响的两个星系，亮度分别只有14和15等，是椭圆螺旋星系，估计离地2.45亿光年，直径均在5.5万光年左右<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc24.htm#2402 | title = NGC Objects: NGC 2400 – 2449 | work = Celestial Atlas | last = Seligman | first = Courtney | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115113451/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc24.htm#2402 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-01-15}}</ref>。

=== 流星雨 ===
[[小犬座流星雨|小犬座流星雨]]又称南河三流星雨<ref>{{cite book | last = Jenniskens | first = Peter | title = Meteor Showers and Their Parent Comets | pages = 200, 769 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 2006 | isbn = 978-0-521-85349-1}}</ref>，是1964年基思·辛德利（{{lang|en|Keith Hindley}}）在五等星水位二附近发现的[[流星雨|流星雨]]。辛德利研究轨迹后推断流星雨和D/1917 F1慧星系出同源，<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Hindley | first1 = K. B. | last2 = Houlden | first2 = M. A. | doi = 10.1038/2251232a0 | title = The 11 Canis Minorids—A New Meteor Stream Probably Associated with Comet Mellish 1917 I | journal = Nature | volume = 225 | issue = 5239 | pages = 1232–1233 | year = 1970 | pmid = 16057004 | bibcode = 1970Natur.225.1232H}}</ref>但未获学界认可，因为他研究的轨迹数量少而且过于分散，不足以确认关联<ref>{{cite journal | title = Meteor Showers of Comet C/1917 F1 Mellish | first1 = P. | last1 = Vereš | first2 = L. | last2 = Kornoš | first3 = J. | last3 = Tóth | year = 2011 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | arxiv = 1010.5733 | bibcode = 2011MNRAS.412..511V | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2010.17923.x | volume = 412 | issue = 1 | pages = 511–521}}</ref>。流星雨在12月4日开始，15日结束，10到11日最频繁<ref>{{cite book | last = Levy | first = David H. | title = David Levy's Guide to Observing Meteor Showers | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, England | year = 2007 | page = 122 | isbn = 978-0-521-69691-3 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=jAr7HMnlPGUC&pg=PA122&redir_esc=y | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2022-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220308075004/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=jAr7HMnlPGUC&pg=PA122&redir_esc=y | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

